It all starts

with a

heartwarming

story.

FUKUMARU comes from a true story about an old gramma and her cat fukumaru, the special bond between old grandma and her cat touches countless people. Intending to spread the genuine relationship between pets and humans, the FUKUMARU brand was established.

For

Pets’ More. 

SAFE

SAFETY FIRST.

All our wall-mounted products must pass our strict weight load tests and are requested to use pet-safe material.

Our bowl, wall-mounted and scratching series have passed the European Union CE certification. And all the bowl series have been certified by SGS, the world’s leading testing, inspection and certification company, to be lead-free, mercury-free, and safe for pets.

Every batch of products must pass our quality control before shipping to our customers.

PRACTICAL

CONCISE & USEFUL.

We develop products with simple and practical designs, and focus on the main needs of pets' lives.

Products are developed to satisfy their physical and instinctual needs, effectively improving pets' lives.

NATURAL

ENVIRONMENT-FRIENDLY.

We design products with environmentally friendly, natural and quality materials, using natural A-grade rubber, pine, bamboo and walnut wood.

Finest and odorless lacquer and OSMO oil are used to protect wooden parts and provide a long-lasting finish.

LIVE TOGETHER,

LIVE BETTER.

FUKUMARU

Focus on providing natural safe and practical pet supplies, designed to think a little more for them.
